name: Alex Vega
summary:
Alex Vega, a 35-year-old non-binary Director working in the entertainment industry in Los Angeles, is seeking a long term relationship but is also open to short term. They are a graduate of the University of Michigan, identify as agnostic and liberal, and speak both English and Spanish. 

Originally from Miami, Alex is of Hispanic/Latino ethnicity and prefers using "they/them/their" pronouns. They are an ENFP according to the Myers Briggs Type Indicator and their zodiac sign is Leo. While they do not have any children, they aspire to have them someday. Alex is active and occasionally enjoys a drink but does not consume smoking, marijuana, or any other drugs. In their free time, they indulge in activities like filmmaking, basketball, cooking, and traveling. Family bonds, sustainable living, and creativity are core parts of their personal values. 

Alex is interested in a partner aged between 28 and 40 years who is open to having children in the future. They prefer someone who is non-drinker, non-smoker, does not consume marijuana or engage in drug usage, and leads an active lifestyle. Alex is a cat lover and is hoping to find someone who shares the same penchant for pets.
